org.dolan.datastructures

Interface IProcessedFile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProcessedFile

    public interface IProcessedFile
    The Interface IProcessedFile. IProcessedFile is the file which is returned after being processed. It contains many (or one) ThreadBlock which represents the file.
